data.description: LISTED BELOW APPRAISED VALUE - VA ASSUMABLE FOR VETERANS. Welcome to the sought-after Rebecca Lake community in Whitewater school district! This 4-bedroom with a bonus, 3.5-bath home has tons to offer with 4,592 sq ft of living space. Enjoy spectacular, panoramic views of the private lake from the living room right next to your spacious kitchen that includes stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of cabinet space. The primary bedroom is on the main level and features its own sitting area/office space with a view of the lake. A fully finished, walkout basement offers the flexibility of serving as an in-law suite or additional guest living area and has a lot of storage space. At the back of the property, soak in the natural surroundings as you take a short, tree-covered stroll to the community's pool, tennis courts, and clubhouse. Make this lakeside home yours today!
